Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:08.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I guess I just made things awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:12.58,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I started feeling sorry for myself, and \Nnow I'm causing trouble for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:14.04,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Natori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.40,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Kanie? Why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:21.65,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You were lying about running errands, weren't you?{Changed from "plans" in the last ep. Will update in batch.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:23.30,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No, I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:28.87,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Is it that you really just wanted to be alone with Aida?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:29.44,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:30.86,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:33.14,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You weren't able to turn him \Ndown when he asked you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:35.58,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You certainly didn't seem very upset when he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:44.53,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I told you, that's because he already suspects that... that I'm not Kaho.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:48.27,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,If I avoid him too much, he'll get even more suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:50.74,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:55.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It's not like he has any proof, so what difference does that make?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:57.36,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I mean, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:03.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Just how long do you plan to keep up this ridiculous charade when you're scared of your own shadow?{DO YOU SEE WHAT I DID THERE?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:06.82,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Ridiculous charade," huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:08.90,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That hit the nail on the head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:10.54,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no comeback.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:14.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't mean to come at you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:17.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:19.10,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:20.66,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Done with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:23.18,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:25.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:29.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,"None of my business," is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:37.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,The 25 Year Old High School Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:37.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Episode 11: The Absolute Worst Day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.23,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It's alright, K-Kanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.23,0:01:42.68,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I can get home by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:44.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,So you don't really have any errands, do you?{Changed from "plans" in ep.10--contextually this makes more sense. That episode will get updated in the batch.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:48.21,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.73,0:01:52.61,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one to decide that it's "none of my business."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:54.21,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-Kanie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:02:00.05,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No, Kanie... S-Stop, I mean it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:13.36,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he upset about what I said?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:18.49,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You can say it's "none of my business" all you want, but I can tell how much you're enjoying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:19.99,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:22.37,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:28.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:32.26,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:39.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-I thought that, bit-by-bit, I was starting to really understand him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:42.64,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,...but all it takes is one remark hitting home
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:45.59,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,to set him off like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:46.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.02,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's none of your business.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.74,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.75,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-Natori, I'm sorry. I went too far—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:21.32,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:26.63,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Hasegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:26.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.13,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:28.86,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:30.17,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:30.70,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:31.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:34.48,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Kaho Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:36.16,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:38.86,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi isn't coming in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.03,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:44.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't say I'm surprised.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:55.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:53.69,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh, I guess auntie is out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I even told her I was vising today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:59.80,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really wanted to have a serious conversation about Kaho.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.65,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ended up skipping school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:05.58,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I even doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:11.64,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(56.02,45)}Call History\NKanie\NKanie\NKanie\NKanie\NKanie\NKanie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:09.34,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have so many calls from Kanie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.64,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if he's worried about me after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:14.43,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to have a real talk with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I said some things I regret too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.20,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-Another call?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.51,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Kanie\NMobile
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:20.65,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Natori...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:25.04,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,K-Kanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:29.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1\pos(640,15)}Who could have predicted this reunion?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.91,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1\pos(640,15)}I reel in this thread of memory, and use it to spin my tale{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:37.42,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1\}I reel in this thread of memory, and use it to spin my tale{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:42.31,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why are you all pushy one minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:48.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,and then gentle the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:53.55,Songs,,0,0,0,,As long as the two of us share this secret
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:59.11,Songs,,0,0,0,,it will be the light that guides you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:03.89,Songs,,0,0,0,,to somewhere in the yet-unknowable future
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:08.33,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's okay to be optimistic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:12.37,Songs,,0,0,0,,I want to know everything about you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:17.81,Songs,,0,0,0,,hidden deep within those eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:23.07,Songs,,0,0,0,,I can't control these feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:30.23,Songs,,0,0,0,,Piece by piece, my heart is being snatched away
